    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="install-nodejs"><a href="#install-nodejs" class="headerlink" title="install nodejs"></a>install nodejs</h2><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/</a><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ curl <span class="_">-s</span>L https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -</div><div class="line">$ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs</div><div class="line">$ sudo apt-get install -y build-essential</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="install-hexo"><a href="#install-hexo" class="headerlink" title="install hexo"></a>install hexo</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo npm install hexo-cli -g</div><div class="line">$ sudo npm install hexo --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="hexo-init"><a href="#hexo-init" class="headerlink" title="hexo init"></a>hexo init</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo init  &lt;folder&gt;</div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>###install plugin<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-index --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-archive --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-category --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-tag --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-server --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-heroku --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-rsync --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-openshift --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-renderer-marked@0.2 --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-renderer-stylus@0.2 --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-feed@1 --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-sitemap@1 --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="create-youre-repo-on-github"><a href="#create-youre-repo-on-github" class="headerlink" title="create youre repo on github"></a>create youre repo on github</h2><p>xxx.github.io<br>enable GitHub Pages<br><a href="https://github.com/xxx/xxx.github.io/settings" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/xxx/xxx.github.io/settings</a></p>
<h2 id="init-git-and-ssh"><a href="#init-git-and-ssh" class="headerlink" title="init git and ssh"></a>init git and ssh</h2><p>gen and upload public key<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C <span class="string">"xxx@xxx.com"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>set git config<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git config --global user.name xxx</div><div class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"xxx@xxx.com"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="custom-your-blog-config"><a href="#custom-your-blog-config" class="headerlink" title="custom your blog config"></a>custom your blog config</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ vim _config.yml</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>language: zh-CN<br>timezone: Asia/Shanghai<br>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: git@github.com:xxx/xxx.github.io.git<br>  branch: master</p>
<h2 id="write-new-blog-page"><a href="#write-new-blog-page" class="headerlink" title="write new blog page"></a>write new blog page</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new  write_blog_by_hexo_2_github</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Gen-static-blog-and-Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Gen-static-blog-and-Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Gen static blog and Deploy to remote sites"></a>Gen static blog and Deploy to remote sites</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line">$ hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="hexo-命令"><a href="#hexo-命令" class="headerlink" title="hexo 命令"></a>hexo 命令</h2><p>hexo n #生成文章，或者手动编辑<br>hexo s #本地发布预览效果  <a href="http://127.0.0.1:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://127.0.0.1:4000/</a><br>hexo g #生成public静态文件<br>hexo d #部署</p>
<h2 id="refs"><a href="#refs" class="headerlink" title="refs:"></a>refs:</h2><p><a href="https://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/</a><br><a href="http://www.tuicool.com/articles/ueI7naV" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.tuicool.com/articles/ueI7naV</a><br><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/</a></p>
]]></content>
    
